headline: HP Inc. Declares Dividend
summary: PALO ALTO, Calif., Jan. 27, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- HP Inc. (NYSE: HPQ) has declared a cash dividend of $0.3000 per share on the company’s common stock. The dividend, the second in HP’s fiscal year 2026, is payable on April 1, 2026, to stockholders of record as of the close of business on March 11, 2026.
